developed a new Stand.

00:01:15.009 --> 00:01:16.844 position:5% line:89% align:start
[mechanical clanking, whirring]

00:01:23.250 --> 00:01:24.886 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
In order for human beings

00:01:24.919 --> 00:01:26.386 position:21% line:89% align:start
