00:01:26.420 --> 00:01:28.990 position:16% line:83% align:start
they must first overcome
their destiny.

00:01:29.023 --> 00:01:32.192 position:24% line:83% align:start
And the obstacles
Dio and I must overcome

00:01:32.225 --> 00:01:34.963 position:19% line:83% align:start
