and your bloodline.

00:01:34.996 --> 00:01:36.129 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:01:36.698 --> 00:01:37.732 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:01:37.765 --> 00:01:39.834 position:30% line:89% align:start
