00:01:41.703 --> 00:01:43.705 position:21% line:89% align:start
[See Moon grumbles]

00:01:46.074 --> 00:01:48.175 position:33% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:01:49.577 --> 00:01:50.678 position:35% line:89% align:start
[retches]

00:01:50.712 --> 00:01:52.547 position:38% line:89% align:start
[cracks]

00:01:52.580 --> 00:01:54.882 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Her heart has
been turned inside out.

00:01:54.916 --> 00:01:57.752 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:02:03.925 --> 00:02:05.627 position:24% line:89% align:start
