00:02:05.660 --> 00:02:08.228 position:21% line:89% align:start
My phone... But how?

00:02:08.261 --> 00:02:09.864 position:13% line:89% align:start
It wasn't working before.

00:02:11.766 --> 00:02:13.400 position:10% line:89% align:start
Could this text be from...?

00:02:14.068 --> 00:02:15.369 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Jotaro] Jolyne is alive,

00:02:16.037 --> 00:02:17.538 position:27% line:89% align:start
but just barely.

00:02:18.673 --> 00:02:20.708 position:16% line:89% align:start
Yeah, it is Mr. Jotaro!

00:02:20.742 --> 00:02:22.476 position:21% line:89% align:start
He must be close by.

00:02:22.510 --> 00:02:25.212 position:35% line:83% align:start
Anastasia,
you gotta find Jolyne!

00:02:25.245 --> 00:02:27.247 position:21% line:83% align:start
I think that Jolyne
is still alive!

00:02:28.082 --> 00:02:29.449 position:35% line:89% align:start
