00:02:29.483 --> 00:02:32.086 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
What's going on? Jolyne Cujoh!

00:02:32.120 --> 00:02:34.488 position:16% line:83% align:start
Her heart should've been
turned inside out!

00:02:34.522 --> 00:02:36.423 position:7% line:89% align:start
I have to put an end to this.

00:02:36.456 --> 00:02:38.860 position:19% line:83% align:start
The Joestar bloodline
is something I must overcome,

00:02:38.893 --> 00:02:40.260 position:16% line:89% align:start
