00:02:43.463 --> 00:02:45.198 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whimpers]

00:02:45.967 --> 00:02:48.402 position:5% line:89% align:start
But... Which way are you going?

00:02:49.169 --> 00:02:51.204 position:10% line:89% align:start
In order to protect Jolyne,

00:02:51.238 --> 00:02:53.473 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna have to kill
that fucking priest!

00:02:54.642 --> 00:02:56.844 position:30% line:89% align:start
[theme music]

00:04:27.568 --> 00:04:29.203 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Jolyne...

00:04:29.237 --> 00:04:30.972 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm well aware that
she doesn't have

00:04:31.005 --> 00:04:32.507 position:24% line:83% align:start
