move her body,

00:04:32.540 --> 00:04:33.775 position:10% line:89% align:start
but how is she still alive?

00:04:34.876 --> 00:04:37.410 position:24% line:83% align:start
Did I somehow miss
her vital points by accident?

00:04:37.712 --> 00:04:38.513 position:44% line:89% align:start
No.

00:04:40.081 --> 00:04:42.150 position:27% line:83% align:start
Without a doubt,
I hit her heart dead on.

00:04:42.183 --> 00:04:43.818 position:21% line:83% align:start
It should've turned
inside out.

00:04:44.752 --> 00:04:47.454 position:30% line:83% align:start
Could this be
the Joestar bloodline,

00:04:47.487 --> 00:04:49.657 position:30% line:83% align:start
and the blood
of that damn Kujo?

00:04:49.690 --> 00:04:51.626 position:19% line:83% align:start
Is that what's trying
to hinder the plan

00:04:51.659 --> 00:04:53.594 position:5% line:83% align:start
that Dio and I had been working
to achieve?

00:04:53.628 --> 00:04:55.328 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:04:56.864 --> 00:04:59.332 position:27% line:83% align:start
It's imperative
that I end Jolyne Cujoh here,

00:04:59.366 --> 00:05:02.236 position:19% line:83% align:start
no matter what lengths
I must go to.

00:05:02.270 --> 00:05:04.639 position:16% line:83% align:start
All the times Jolyne has
interfered with my plan,

00:05:04.672 --> 00:05:06.774 position:24% line:83% align:start
within the prison
and in Orlando,

00:05:06.808 --> 00:05:08.910 position:27% line:83% align:start
have been tests
on my path to heaven!

00:05:11.179 --> 00:05:15.382 position:19% line:83% align:start
I know I can do this.
I'm Father Pucchi.

00:05:15.415 --> 00:05:19.386 position:5% line:83% align:start
I am the one who walks the path
with fate on my side.

00:05:19.419 --> 00:05:21.789 position:21% line:83% align:start
Our plan goes beyond
petty feelings of justice.

00:05:22.422 --> 00:05:24.759 position:16% line:89% align:start
Dio and I will succeed!

00:05:24.792 --> 00:05:27.895 position:5% line:83% align:start
There isn't a soul in the world
capable of getting in our way.

00:05:27.929 --> 00:05:29.797 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's simply inconceivable!

00:05:31.132 --> 00:05:34.535 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunts]
You there... please, help me.

00:05:34.569 --> 00:05:37.305 position:10% line:83% align:start
I could really use a doctor.
[groans]

00:05:37.337 --> 00:05:39.240 position:19% line:83% align:start
I think my hip bone's
pretty messed up.

00:05:39.273 --> 00:05:41.374 position:13% line:89% align:start
Can you call an ambulance?

00:05:41.408 --> 00:05:44.011 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[Father Pucchi scoffs]
-Please, don't leave me!

00:05:44.045 --> 00:05:46.581 position:7% line:89% align:start
It is close. I'm almost there.

00:05:46.614 --> 00:05:49.482 position:10% line:83% align:start
The place where Jolyne fell
should be around here.

00:05:59.227 --> 00:06:00.360 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:06:02.429 --> 00:06:05.833 position:10% line:83% align:start
She's there. That's a scrap
of Jolyne's clothing.

00:06:05.867 --> 00:06:07.335 position:21% line:83% align:start
Meaning, it's likely
that she wound up

00:06:07.367 --> 00:06:08.836 position:10% line:89% align:start
falling into this building.

00:06:10.470 --> 00:06:12.405 position:27% line:83% align:start
As for the fool
sneaking up behind me,

00:06:12.439 --> 00:06:14.876 position:19% line:83% align:start
I suggest you not come
any closer.

00:06:14.909 --> 00:06:16.911 position:21% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music]

00:06:18.913 --> 00:06:22.116 position:38% line:83% align:start
Go away.
I do not consider you a test.

00:06:22.149 --> 00:06:24.417 position:21% line:83% align:start
You don't even pose
a threat to me.

00:06:26.621 --> 00:06:28.990 position:13% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music builds]

00:06:32.126 --> 00:06:33.527 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yelps]

00:06:34.427 --> 00:06:35.796 position:35% line:89% align:start
[retches]

00:06:37.131 --> 00:06:39.166 position:21% line:89% align:start
[flesh rips, cracks]

00:06:39.200 --> 00:06:40.368 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gags]

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:41.535 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:06:41.569 --> 00:06:43.137 position:21% line:89% align:start
Fall back, See Moon!

00:06:43.170 --> 00:06:44.505 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's not Anastasia!

00:06:46.439 --> 00:06:48.376 position:27% line:89% align:start
