00:06:48.408 --> 00:06:50.611 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:06:50.645 --> 00:06:51.512 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:06:52.947 --> 00:06:55.182 position:19% line:83% align:start
Diver Drive can phase
into more than

00:06:55.216 --> 00:06:58.019 position:13% line:83% align:start
