from the inside,

00:07:03.456 --> 00:07:04.892 position:16% line:89% align:start
and turned him into me.

00:07:04.926 --> 00:07:05.693 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:05.726 --> 00:07:07.995 position:24% line:83% align:start
And you're already
within my range.

00:07:08.029 --> 00:07:11.498 position:16% line:89% align:start
Take this! Diver Drive!

00:07:12.300 --> 00:07:14.001 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] I-I missed!

00:07:14.035 --> 00:07:16.804 position:30% line:83% align:start
The madman...
He turned himself inside out!

00:07:19.707 --> 00:07:21.075 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
To me, your significance

00:07:21.108 --> 00:07:22.977 position:24% line:83% align:start
your significance
is even less than Sun Wukong

00:07:23.010 --> 00:07:25.913 position:21% line:83% align:start
as he bounced around
in the Buddha's hand.

00:07:25.947 --> 00:07:26.948 position:24% line:89% align:start
[exclaims, gasps]

00:07:26.981 --> 00:07:28.849 position:27% line:89% align:start
[See Moon roars]

00:07:33.287 --> 00:07:34.722 position:30% line:89% align:start
[gasps slowly]

00:07:36.157 --> 00:07:37.525 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:38.726 --> 00:07:40.194 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:40.227 --> 00:07:42.495 position:30% line:89% align:start
[tense music]

00:07:42.530 --> 00:07:43.931 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:07:45.900 --> 00:07:46.901 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunts]
Huh?

00:07:50.404 --> 00:07:52.406 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
Something just touched my face.

00:07:52.440 --> 00:07:54.575 position:7% line:89% align:start
That was Jolyne Cujoh's hand.

00:07:54.608 --> 00:07:56.110 position:30% line:89% align:start
She's moving.

00:07:57.078 --> 00:07:59.213 position:13% line:83% align:start
What on God's green earth
is she doing?

00:07:59.246 --> 00:08:01.048 position:7% line:89% align:start
