00:08:01.082 --> 00:08:02.883 position:13% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music builds]

00:08:03.351 --> 00:08:04.919 position:27% line:89% align:start
She's bleeding.

00:08:04.952 --> 00:08:07.455 position:21% line:83% align:start
She must've suffered
a grave injury.

00:08:07.487 --> 00:08:08.689 position:10% line:89% align:start
My heart is telling me that

00:08:08.723 --> 00:08:10.958 position:24% line:83% align:start
I must pursue her
with everything I have.

00:08:11.359 --> 00:08:12.593 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:08:12.626 --> 00:08:15.629 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now is the time
to end her permanently!

00:08:16.597 --> 00:08:18.599 position:16% line:89% align:start
[approaching footsteps]

00:08:31.012 --> 00:08:32.113 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi exclaims]

00:08:32.146 --> 00:08:33.447 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi] Given that
he'll be looking

00:08:33.481 --> 00:08:34.415 position:24% line:89% align:start
for his daughter,

00:08:34.448 --> 00:08:35.649 position:21% line:89% align:start
I have no doubt that

00:08:35.683 --> 00:08:38.719 position:21% line:83% align:start
Jotaro Kujo will be
arriving here any moment.

00:08:38.753 --> 00:08:42.123 position:5% line:83% align:start
And it'll be a real nuisance if
Anastasia regains his composure

00:08:42.156 --> 00:08:43.791 position:5% line:89% align:start
and tries to come for me again.

00:08:44.291 --> 00:08:45.559 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Emporio grunts]

00:08:46.560 --> 00:08:47.595 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
It appears that

00:08:47.628 --> 00:08:49.530 position:19% line:83% align:start
everyone is gathering
to this location

00:08:49.563 --> 00:08:52.099 position:21% line:83% align:start
in order to protect
Jolyne Cujoh.

00:08:53.234 --> 00:08:54.435 position:21% line:89% align:start
If that is the case,

00:08:54.468 --> 00:08:57.872 position:7% line:83% align:start
what's most significant right
now is that you perish here.

00:08:57.905 --> 00:09:00.408 position:16% line:83% align:start
They all believe in you,
but it is your death

00:09:00.441 --> 00:09:02.109 position:24% line:83% align:start
that will shatter
the hearts of everyone

00:09:02.143 --> 00:09:02.977 position:16% line:89% align:start
who's heading this way.

00:09:03.010 --> 00:09:03.611 position:27% line:83% align:start
[dramatic music]
who's heading this way.

00:09:03.644 --> 00:09:04.311 position:27% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music]

00:09:06.947 --> 00:09:09.950 position:24% line:83% align:start
