who'll be losing his daughter.

00:09:09.984 --> 00:09:11.952 position:16% line:83% align:start
That should be enough to
strip him of his reason to live

00:09:11.986 --> 00:09:13.587 position:7% line:89% align:start
and the strength in his heart.

00:09:16.624 --> 00:09:19.693 position:7% line:83% align:start
He will no longer be a threat
to either me or Dio.

00:09:19.727 --> 00:09:23.564 position:24% line:83% align:start
It has to be now,
in this very place!

00:09:23.597 --> 00:09:25.966 position:27% line:83% align:start
I will find you,
no matter what it takes!

00:09:32.206 --> 00:09:33.174 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:09:38.946 --> 00:09:41.816 position:10% line:89% align:start
Show yourself, Jolyne Cujoh!

00:09:41.849 --> 00:09:43.818 position:16% line:89% align:start
You can't hide anymore!

00:09:45.052 --> 00:09:46.253 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:09:46.287 --> 00:09:47.721 position:19% line:89% align:start
There you are, Jolyne!

00:09:48.422 --> 00:09:49.757 position:24% line:89% align:start
[See Moon screams]

00:09:51.560 --> 00:09:53.761 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi gasps]
It's just her strings.

00:09:53.794 --> 00:09:55.663 position:16% line:83% align:start
Dammit, she's behind me!
[grunts]

00:09:55.996 --> 00:09:57.298 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chokes]

00:09:57.331 --> 00:09:58.866 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi grunts]

00:09:58.899 --> 00:10:01.001 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:10:01.035 --> 00:10:02.837 position:21% line:83% align:start
I am going to devote
my entire being

00:10:02.870 --> 00:10:04.905 position:27% line:83% align:start
to snuffing out
your life right here!

00:10:04.939 --> 00:10:07.641 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm already aware you've
suffered a severe injury!

00:10:10.277 --> 00:10:12.413 position:24% line:83% align:start
The gravity pulls
in the opposite direction

00:10:12.446 --> 00:10:14.315 position:16% line:89% align:start
of wherever my feet are!

00:10:14.348 --> 00:10:15.816 position:10% line:89% align:start
Everything falls towards me!

00:10:15.850 --> 00:10:18.686 position:21% line:89% align:start
[tense action music]

00:10:18.719 --> 00:10:19.887 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi] See Moon!

00:10:23.090 --> 00:10:25.493 position:27% line:83% align:start
There, I got you
with a direct hit!

00:10:25.527 --> 00:10:27.828 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now both of your arms
are as good as gone!

00:10:34.268 --> 00:10:35.336 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi exclaims]

00:10:35.369 --> 00:10:37.171 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic choral music]

00:10:44.078 --> 00:10:44.945 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:46.647 --> 00:10:47.715 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:10:50.251 --> 00:10:52.554 position:10% line:89% align:start
What in the world was that?

00:10:52.587 --> 00:10:54.955 position:27% line:83% align:start
Both of her arms
should've been inverted!

00:10:56.690 --> 00:10:58.025 position:30% line:89% align:start
What the hell?

00:10:59.093 --> 00:11:01.662 position:27% line:89% align:start
[blood gurgling]

00:11:05.065 --> 00:11:07.434 position:5% line:89% align:start
Come on out! Now, Jolyne Cujoh!

00:11:07.468 --> 00:11:11.138 position:16% line:83% align:start
Your attempts to stop me
are futile! You can't get away!

00:11:11.172 --> 00:11:12.773 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne strains]

00:11:13.174 --> 00:11:16.143 position:35% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:11:16.177 --> 00:11:17.878 position:24% line:89% align:start
[breathes heavily]

