00:20:21.556 --> 00:20:23.490 position:10% line:89% align:start
What the hell just happened?

00:20:23.524 --> 00:20:25.560 position:13% line:89% align:start
The spear missed its mark.

00:20:25.593 --> 00:20:26.994 position:24% line:83% align:start
He moved slightly
during the time stop.

00:20:27.729 --> 00:20:29.530 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Emporio shudders]

00:20:29.564 --> 00:20:31.899 position:10% line:89% align:start
It failed. He's still alive.

00:20:33.266 --> 00:20:34.769 position:19% line:89% align:start
He's opening the door.

00:20:34.802 --> 00:20:37.437 position:10% line:83% align:start
It looks like he's trying to
get inside the Space Shuttle.

00:20:38.438 --> 00:20:39.574 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Ermes] Yeah,
and now this thing

00:20:39.607 --> 00:20:41.408 position:21% line:83% align:start
is starting to float
in the air too!

00:20:43.611 --> 00:20:44.612 position:10% line:89% align:start
The priest is taking shelter

00:20:44.645 --> 00:20:46.981 position:33% line:83% align:start
in a goddamn
displaced Space Shuttle!

00:20:48.816 --> 00:20:52.285 position:7% line:83% align:start
He managed to avoid the spear,
but how?

00:20:52.319 --> 00:20:53.688 position:24% line:89% align:start
It makes no sense.

00:20:54.254 --> 00:20:55.623 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hey, you guys...

00:20:55.656 --> 00:20:57.859 position:30% line:83% align:start
I don't think
he's just trying to get away.

00:20:58.458 --> 00:21:00.995 position:16% line:89% align:start
It can't be. Did he...?

00:21:02.063 --> 00:21:03.463 position:30% line:83% align:start
Could he have
discovered something

00:21:03.497 --> 00:21:05.465 position:24% line:83% align:start
that's giving him
the advantage?

00:21:05.499 --> 00:21:07.802 position:21% line:83% align:start
Did he actually find
the missing element

00:21:07.835 --> 00:21:09.137 position:16% line:89% align:start
to complete his ability?

00:21:09.170 --> 00:21:10.370 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:21:11.205 --> 00:21:13.340 position:24% line:89% align:start
[grandiose music]

00:21:26.254 --> 00:21:27.989 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Father Pucchi cackles]

00:21:28.022 --> 00:21:29.223 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
You are the ones

00:21:29.257 --> 00:21:31.358 position:21% line:83% align:start
who've been helping
to raise me up all along.

00:21:32.160 --> 00:21:33.761 position:7% line:89% align:start
Ever since you were in prison,

00:21:33.795 --> 00:21:35.730 position:24% line:83% align:start
you've been there,
lending me aid!

00:21:36.597 --> 00:21:37.330 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:21:39.033 --> 00:21:40.668 position:7% line:89% align:start
Our Father, who art in heaven,

00:21:40.701 --> 00:21:43.037 position:30% line:83% align:start
I beseech you
to lead and guide me!

00:21:44.238 --> 00:21:46.507 position:21% line:83% align:start
I ask you to please
watch over me,

00:21:46.541 --> 00:21:49.510 position:19% line:83% align:start
so I may not walk down
the wrong path!

00:21:49.544 --> 00:21:53.648 position:16% line:83% align:start
It is to your very will
that I shall dedicate myself!

00:21:54.715 --> 00:21:56.083 position:30% line:89% align:start
I can feel it!

00:21:59.153 --> 00:22:01.354 position:24% line:89% align:start
[grandiose music]

00:22:05.059 --> 00:22:07.695 position:13% line:89% align:start
The coordinates! I'm here!

00:22:10.665 --> 00:22:13.433 position:24% line:83% align:start
["Distant Dreamer"
by Duffy playing]

